            <p style="margin-bottom: 2rem; font-size: 1.1rem;">Once you've completed the checklist, please submit your feedback:</p>
            <a href="/beta-feedback.html" class="cta-button" style="background: white; color: #1a4d2e; padding: 1.25rem 2.5rem; border-radius: 12px; font-weight: 700; text-decoration: none; font-size: 1.1rem;">
